name: Central Park Romantic Stroll
description: One Stop for Central Park..Most people think Central Park is just that....A Park, BUT.. it's so much more.  From the Bike Tours . to visiting the Statues of Balto and Alice in Wonderland, the Boat House and row boats.  Olympic size swimming pool, Museums,The Mall and especially The Angels over the Fountain at Bethesda Terrace, which is featured in many movies.  Also, the Movie famous, Bow Bridge.  See where major Stars live surrounding Central Park West and East.
